sequenceDiagram
    title KERAS MODEL GRADE PREDICTOR
    actor Student
    participant Profile
    participant Dashboard
    participant RouteManager
    participant RoutineManager
    participant GradePredictor
    participant Supabase

    Student->>Profile: Enter data dictionary & course info
    Profile ->> RouteManager: API request to store data
    RouteManager->>Supabase: Store info
    Supabase -->>RouteManager: Acknowledge storage
    RouteManager -->> Profile: Confirmation message
    Profile-->>Student: Confirmation message

    rect rgb(230, 242, 255)
        Note over GradePredictor, Supabase: Weekly Process
        RoutineManager ->> Supabase: Retrieve Data
        Supabase -->> RoutineManager: Student's data dictionary
        RoutineManager ->> GradePredictor: Student's data dictionary
        GradePredictor -->> RoutineManager: Predicted grade
        RoutineManager ->> Supabase: Store predicted grade
        Supabase -->>RoutineManager: Acknowledge storage
    end

    Student ->> Dashboard: Opens dashboard
    Dashboard ->> RouteManager:API request to retrieve predicted grade
    RouteManager ->> Supabase: Retrieve data
    Supabase -->> RouteManager: Student's predicted grade
    RouteManager -->> Dashboard: Student's predicted grade
    Dashboard -->> Student: Course info along with predicted grade


